msgid "&gnucash; Importer"
msgstr "&gnucash; Uvoznik"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gnucash; Files"
msgstr "&gnucash; Datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kmymoney; &gnucash; importer is known to handle direct reading of "
"standard (&XML;) files as produced by &gnucash; versions 1.8 and 2.0. File "
"from more recent versions should also be imported without problem. There is "
"no recent, formal testing to confirm this, but the developers' mailing list "
"&devlist; has a report of success importing a file from &gnucash; 5.3. "
"Specifically, however, the following are not supported:"
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; &gnucash; znano je, da uvoznik obravnava neposredno branje "
"standardnih (&XML;) datotek, kot jih ustvari &gnucash; različici 1.8 in 2.0. "
"Datoteko iz novejših različic je prav tako moč uvoziti brez težav. Sicer ni "
"nedavnega formalnega testiranja, ki bi to potrdilo, vendar pa poštni seznam "
"razvijalcev &devlist; ima poročilo o uspešnem uvozu datoteke iz &gnucash; "
"5.3. Natančno pa ni podprto naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "import of database (Postgres) data"
msgstr "uvoz podatkov baze (Postgres)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "import of 'multi-book' files"
msgstr "uvoz datotek z več knjigami"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "import into an existing &kmymoney; file"
msgstr "uvoz v obstoječo datoteko &kmymoney;"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "import of small-business specific features (Employees, Invoices, &etc;)"
msgstr "uvoz funkcij, specifičnih za mala podjetja (zaposleni, računi &etc;)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "export to &gnucash; files."
msgstr "izvoz v datoteke &gnucash;."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The import will probably only work correctly if presented with a valid file. "
"It is recommended that the <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Check &amp; Repair All</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item of &gnucash; be run before saving the file and attempting to import "
"into &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Uvoz bo verjetno deloval pravilno le, če bo prejel veljavno datoteko. "
"Priporočljivo je, da zaženete postavko menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri &amp; popravi vse</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"&gnucash; preden shranite datoteko in poskusite uvoziti v &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Files can be opened by specifying the filename on the command line "
"(<command>kmymoney &lt;path to file&gt;</command>), or by means of the "
"&kmymoney; <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice> or <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> menu items."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke lahko odprete z navedbo imena datoteke v ukazni vrstici "
"(<command>kmymoney &lt;pot do datoteke&gt;</command>) ali s pomočjo ukaza "
"&kmymoney; <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut>, elementov menija <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali <menuchoice > "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Uvoz</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The similarity between the two products means that much day-to-day data can "
"be imported in a straightforward fashion. However, there are some areas "
"where there are differences, and various options are provided to deal with "
"these. The following sections will describe some of these differences; "
"understanding them should lead to a smoother import, where any of them are "
"relevant to your data."
msgstr ""
"Podobnost med obema izdelkoma pomeni, da je mogoče uvoziti veliko "
"vsakodnevnih podatkov na preprost način. Vendar obstajajo nekatera področja, "
"kjer obstajajo razlike, in na voljo so različne možnosti za njihovo "
"reševanje. Naslednji razdelki bodo opisali nekatere od teh razlik; njihovo "
"razumevanje bi moralo voditi do bolj gladkega uvoza, kjer je katerikoli od "
"njih pomemben za vaše podatke."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Similarities, Differences, and Terminology"
msgstr "Podobnosti, razlike in terminologija"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Small Business Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba v malih podjetjih"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It should be noted that &kmymoney; is a <emphasis>personal</emphasis> "
"finance manager, and as such, does not directly support any of the business "
"features of &gnucash;, such as tax tables, payroll, and tracking of lots. "
"Any Accounts Payable or Receivable accounts found in a file will be imported "
"as Liability or Asset accounts respectively."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevati je treba, da je &kmymoney; upravljalnik <emphasis>osebnih</"
"emphasis> financ in kot tak neposredno ne podpira nobene poslovne funkcije "
"&gnucash;, kot so davčne tabele, plačilne liste in sledenje sklopom. Vsi "
"računi obveznosti ali terjatev, najdeni v datoteki, bodo uvoženi kot računi "
"obveznosti oziroma imetij."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accounts"
msgstr "Računi"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account types"
msgstr "Vrste računov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For both products, the highest level of structure in the file is the "
"account. &kmymoney; supports 5 main types of account: Asset, Liability, "
"Income, Expense, and Equity, each of which may have various subtypes, &eg;, "
"Checking, Credit Card, &etc; &kmymoney; includes a 'standard' account for "
"each of these five types, and all other accounts are held subordinate to one "
"of these. &kmymoney; enforces more consistency (or less flexibility, "
"depending on your point of view) between account types than does &gnucash;, "
"and the importer will correct any inconsistencies it detects. This may "
"result in a slightly different account structure, though this can, within "
"reason, be amended after the import is complete."
msgstr ""
"Pri obeh izdelkih je najvišja raven strukture v datoteki račun. &kmymoney; "
"podpira 5 glavnih vrst računov: imetja, obveznosti, prihodki, odhodki in "
"lastniški kapital, od katerih ima lahko vsak različne podvrste, npr. tekoči "
"račun, kreditna kartica itd. &kmymoney; vključuje 'standardni' račun za "
"vsako od teh petih vrst, vsi drugi računi pa so podrejeni enemu od teh. "
"&kmymoney; uveljavlja več doslednosti (ali manj prilagodljivosti, odvisno od "
"vašega stališča) med vrstami računov kot &gnucash;, in uvoznik bo popravil "
"vse neskladnosti, ki jih zazna. Posledica tega je lahko nekoliko drugačna "
"struktura računa, čeprav je to mogoče v razumnih mejah spremeniti, ko je "
"uvoz končan."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Categories"
msgstr "Kategorije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; uses the term Category to denote an account of an Income or "
"Expense type. Unlike &gnucash;, these are not considered as <quote>ledger</"
"quote> accounts, and entry of transactions directly into categories is not "
"supported. Allocations to Categories are made when transactions are entered "
"or edited in other account types."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; uporablja izraz Kategorija za označevanje računa vrste Prihodek "
"ali Odhodek. Za razliko od &gnucash; se ti ne obravnavajo kot računi "
"<quote>glavne knjige</quote> in vnos transakcij neposredno v kategorije ni "
"podprt. Dodelitve v kategorije se izvedejo, ko se transakcije vnašajo ali "
"urejajo v drugih vrstah računov."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Structure and Placeholders"
msgstr "Struktura in rubrike"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gnucash; supports the use of Placeholder accounts. In effect, these are "
"just read-only accounts into which no transactions can be entered, but which "
"function in an analogous fashion to folders in a folder structure, as a "
"holder for other accounts. Though &kmymoney; does not support this feature "
"as such, it does provide a parent/child account relationship, so the "
"importer simulates placeholders by creating empty accounts."
msgstr ""
"&gnucash; podpira uporabo nadomestnih računov. Dejansko so to le računi samo "
"za branje, v katere ni mogoče vnašati nobenih transakcij, vendar delujejo na "
"podoben način kot mape v strukturi map kot imetnik za druge račune. Čeprav "
"&kmymoney; ne podpira te funkcije kot take, zagotavlja razmerje nadrejeni/"
"podrejeni račun, tako da uvoznik simulira rubrike z ustvarjanjem praznih "
"računov."

