#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transactions and Splits"
msgstr "Transakcije in razcepitve"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balanced transactions"
msgstr "Uravnotežene transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In both programs, data is entered in the form of transactions, each "
"generally consisting of 2 or more split entries. In fact, valid &gnucash; "
"transactions will always contain at least 2 splits, and to conform to "
"&gnucash;'s double-entry bookkeeping standard, these must be in monetary "
"balance (&ie;, they must balance out to zero). &kmymoney; encourages, but "
"does not enforce, this standard, but any imported transaction which is not "
"balanced will be marked in the Ledgers View as having a problem."
msgstr ""
"V obeh programih se podatki vnašajo v obliki transakcij, ki so običajno "
"sestavljene iz 2 ali več ločenih vnosov. Pravzaprav je veljaven &gnucash; "
"transakcije bodo vedno vsebovale vsaj 2 delitvi in ​​za skladnost z &gnucash;"
"ovim standardom dvostavnega knjigovodstva morajo biti te v denarnem stanju "
"(&ie; izravnati se morajo na nič). &kmymoney; spodbuja, vendar ne uveljavlja "
"tega standarda, vendar bo vsaka uvožena transakcija, ki ni uravnotežena, v "
"Pogledu knjig označena kot težavna."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payees"
msgstr "Prejemniki plačil"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; prefers that all transactions have a Payee (a generic term that "
"encompasses both payees and payers,) and unlike &gnucash;, it maintains a "
"list of these payees. Payee names are generated by the importer from the "
"&gnucash; transaction's Description field."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ima raje, da imajo vse transakcije prejemnika plačila (splošen "
"izraz, ki zajema prejemnike plačil in plačnike) in za razliko od &gnucash; "
"vzdržuje seznam teh prejemnikov plačil. Imena prejemnikov plačil ustvari "
"uvoznik iz datoteke &gnucash; polja Opis transakcije."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transfers"
msgstr "Prenosi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; uses the term Transfer to describe a transaction which does not "
"involve a Category, but only transfers money between Asset and/or Liability "
"accounts."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; uporablja izraz Prenos za opis transakcije, ki ne vključuje "
"kategorije, ampak samo prenos denarja med računi sredstev in/ali obveznosti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reconcile"
msgstr "Uskladi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; provides an account reconciliation function similar to that of "
"&gnucash;, and the corresponding transaction status will be imported."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; zagotavlja funkcijo usklajevanja računov, podobno "
"funkciji&gnucash; in ustrezno stanje transakcije bo uvoženo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commodities"
msgstr "Blago"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gnucash; uses the term Commodity to cover both currencies and non-currency "
"assets. These are treated separately in &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"&gnucash; uporablja izraz Blago za valute in nevalute imetij. Ti se v "
"&kmymoney; obravnavajo ločeno."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Currencies"
msgstr "Valute"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; has built-in support for all foreign <link linkend=\"details."
"currencies\">currency</link> types. &kmymoney; also requires that the user "
"specify a base currency, this being the default currency for new accounts. "
"The importer will attempt to determine the most likely base currency, though "
"this choice may be rejected in favor of an alternative."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ima vgrajeno podporo za vse vrste tujih <link linkend=\"details."
"currencies\">valut</link>. &kmymoney; prav tako zahteva, da uporabnik določi "
"osnovno valuto, ki je privzeta valuta za nove račune. Uvoznik bo poskušal "
"določiti najverjetnejšo osnovno valuto, čeprav bo ta izbira lahko zavrnjena "
"v korist druge."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; does not currently support accounts denominated in 'defunct' "
"currencies, except those replaced by the Euro. At present, it will be "
"necessary to remove any such accounts from your &gnucash; file before "
"importing. We hope to improve on this situation in a future release."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; trenutno ne podpira računov, denominiranih v 'nedelujočih' "
"valutah, razen tistih, ki jih je nadomestil evro. Trenutno bo treba vse take "
"račune odstraniti iz vaše datoteke &gnucash; pred uvozom. Upamo, da bomo to "
"situacijo izboljšali v prihodnji izdaji."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Securities and Investments"
msgstr "Vrednostni papirji in naložbe"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Non-currency assets (typically stocks and bonds) are called Securities by "
"&kmymoney;, and represent the main difference between the two products, in "
"that &kmymoney; requires any account denominated in a security to be "
"subordinate to an Investment Account. This is described in more detail in "
"the chapter on <link linkend=\"details.investments\">Investments</link>. "
"Though users may have implemented such a relationship, &gnucash; imposes no "
"defined structure on it, so the importer is unable to detect it and perform "
"an automatic conversion. Three options are therefore made available:"
msgstr ""
"Nevalutna imetja (običajno delnice in obveznice) &kmymoney; imenuje "
"vrednostni papirji in predstavljajo glavno razliko med produktoma, saj "
"&kmymoney; zahteva, da je vsak račun, denominiran v vrednostnem papirju, "
"podrejen naložbenemu računu. To je podrobneje opisano v poglavju <link "
"linkend=\"details.investments\">Naložbe</link>. Čeprav so uporabniki morda "
"implementirali takšno razmerje, ji &gnucash; ne naloži definirane strukture, "
"zato je uvoznik ne more zaznati in izvesti samodejne pretvorbe. Na voljo so "
"torej tri možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a separate Investment account for each security, with the same name "
"as the security"
msgstr ""
"Za vsak vrednostni papir ustvarite ločen naložbeni račun z enakim imenom kot "
"vrednostni papir"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a single Investment account which will act as <quote>parent</quote> "
"for all security accounts"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite en naložbeni račun, ki bo deloval kot <quote>nadrejeni</quote> za "
"vse račune vrednostnih papirjev"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create several Investment accounts, and assign securities to them as "
"directed by the user."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite več naložbenih računov in jim dodelite vrednostne papirje po "
"navodilih uporabnika."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It depends entirely on user requirements and preference which of these "
"options is relevant in each situation. In some cases, manual restructuring "
"of accounts after import may be necessary."
msgstr ""
"Katera od teh možnosti je ustrezna v posamezni situaciji, je povsem odvisno "
"od uporabnikovih zahtev in preferenc. V nekaterih primerih bo morda potrebno "
"ročno prestrukturiranje računov po uvozu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prices and currency rates"
msgstr "Cene in menjalni tečaji"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Security prices and currency exchange rates, as displayed in the &gnucash; "
"Price Editor, will be imported. In addition, price and rate entries will be "
"generated from all transactions involving securities and multiple currencies."
msgstr ""
"Cene vrednostnih papirjev in menjalni tečaji, kot so prikazani v &gnucash; "
"Urejevalnik cen bo uvožen. Poleg tega bodo vnosi cen in tečajev ustvarjeni "
"iz vseh transakcij, ki vključujejo vrednostne papirje in več valut."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:284 details-impexp.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Quotes"
msgstr "Spletne kotacije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For obtaining online price and currency rate quotations, &gnucash; uses a "
"Perl based package called <literal>Finance::Quote</literal>. Recent versions "
"of &kmymoney; contain support for this package for obtaining stock quotes, "
"and this will be used by default when importing data from &gnucash;. You may "
"however select to convert to the native method used by &kmymoney; which is "
"covered in more detail in the section on <link linkend=\"details.investments."
"onlinequotes\">online quotes</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za pridobivanje spletnih kotacij cen in valutnih tečajev &gnucash; uporablja "
"paket, ki temelji na Perlu, imenovan <literal>Finance::Quote</literal>. "
"Zadnje različice &kmymoney; vsebujejo podporo za ta paket za pridobivanje "
"borznih kotacij, ki bo privzeto uporabljen pri uvažanju podatkov iz "
"&gnucash;. Lahko pa izberete pretvorbo v izvirno metodo, ki jo uporablja "
"&kmymoney; ki je podrobneje obravnavan v razdelku o <link linkend=\"details."
"investments.onlinequotes\">spletnih kotacijah</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose to do so, the following dialog will allow selection of a "
"<quote>native</quote> &kmymoney; price source, or a user-defined source, for "
"each account for which online quotes are required. However, the stock "
"(ticker) symbol will be imported unchanged. Since this symbol will almost "
"certainly be different in the two packages, it will need to be manually "
"edited after completion of the import process. Future currency rate updates "
"will not use <literal>Finance::Quote</literal>, and will always use the "
"native retrieval method."
msgstr ""
"Če se tako odločite, bo naslednje pogovorno okno omogočilo izbiro "
"<quote>izvornega</quote> &kmymoney; cenovni vir ali uporabniško določen vir "
"za vsak račun, za katerega se zahtevajo spletne kotacije. Vendar bo simbol "
"delnice (ticker) uvožen nespremenjen. Ker se bo ta simbol v obeh paketih "
"skoraj zagotovo razlikoval, ga bo treba po zaključku postopka uvoza ročno "
"urediti. Prihodnje posodobitve valutnih tečajev ne bodo uporabljale "
"<literal>Finance::Quote</literal> in bodo vedno uporabljale izvirno metodo "
"pridobivanja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>gnucash import price source selection</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>izbira vira uvoza cene gnucash</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>gnucash import price source selection</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>izbira vira uvoza cene gnucash</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:319 details-impexp.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduled Transactions"
msgstr "Načrtovane transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; does not retain the separation made in &gnucash; between template "
"transactions and their frequency of occurrence. Transaction data will be "
"duplicated if the same template is used in different schedules, but this is "
"not likely to be of great significance."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ne ohrani ločevanja v &gnucash; med šablonskimi transakcijami in "
"njihovo pogostostjo pojavljanja. Podatki o transakcijah se bodo podvojili, "
"če bo ista predloga uporabljena v različnih časovnih načrtih, vendar to "
"verjetno ne bo imelo velikega pomena."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schedule types"
msgstr "Vrste časovnih načrtov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; classifies all schedules as one of three types: Bills, Deposits, "
"or Transfers. Since &gnucash; does not make such a distinction, the importer "
"attempts to determine the classification from the accounts and direction of "
"money movements. It may be that in some cases incorrect assumptions are "
"made, and these will need manual correction."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; razvrsti vse časovne plane v eno od treh vrst: računi, depoziti "
"ali prenosi. Ker tega &gnucash; ne razlikuje, skuša uvoznik razvrstitev "
"ugotoviti iz računov in smeri gibanja denarja. Lahko se zgodi, da so v "
"nekaterih primerih narejene napačne predpostavke, ki jih bo treba ročno "
"popraviti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suspect Schedules"
msgstr "Sumljivi časovni načrti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some features of &gnucash; scheduled transactions are not available in "
"&kmymoney;, so the importer tries in each case to reach a reasonable "
"compromise in converting the data. These transactions will be flagged as "
"suspect, and the user will be given the option of editing them directly "
"during the import process. Examples of situations which may cause this are:"
msgstr ""
"Nekatere funkcije &gnucash; načrtovanih transakcije niso na voljo v "
"&kmymoney;, zato poskuša uvoznik v vsakem primeru doseči razumen kompromis "
"pri pretvorbi podatkov. Te transakcije bodo označene kot sumljive, uporabnik "
"pa bo imel možnost, da jih ureja neposredno med postopkom uvoza. Primeri "
"situacij, ki lahko povzročijo to, so:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"some frequency intervals supported in &gnucash; are not currently available "
"in &kmymoney;"
msgstr ""
"nekateri frekvenčni intervali, podprti v &gnucash; trenutno niso na voljo v "
"&kmymoney;"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; does not support the use of formulae and variables in amount "
"fields"
msgstr "&kmymoney; ne podpira uporabe formul in spremenljivk v poljih z zneski"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "complex cases which have not yet been identified for import"
msgstr "zapleteni primeri, ki še niso bili opredeljeni za uvoz"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Despite best efforts, it is possible that, due to the many options involved, "
"a scheduled transaction may cause a fatal error within &kmymoney;. If this "
"sort of problem seems to be occurring, the importer offers the option to "
"drop all suspect schedules."
msgstr ""
"Kljub vsem prizadevanjem je možno, da zaradi številnih vključenih možnosti "
"načrtovana transakcija povzroči usodno napako v &kmymoney;. Če se zdi, da se "
"pojavlja tovrstna težava, uvoznik ponudi možnost, da opusti vse sumljive "
"časovne načrte."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Poročila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; provides a comprehensive selection of configurable reports, "
"described in more detail in <link linkend=\"details.reports\">Reports.</"
"link> These will not necessarily, however, match precisely those reports "
"available in &gnucash;."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ponuja obsežen izbor nastavljivih poročil, ki so podrobneje "
"opisana v <link linkend=\"details.reports\">Poročilih.</link> Ni pa nujno, "
"da se bodo natančno ujemala s tistimi poročili, ki so na voljo v &gnucash;."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Importer Options"
msgstr "Izbira možnosti uvoznika"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>gnucash import options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>možnosti uvoza gnucash</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>gnucash import options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>možnosti uvoza gnucash</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investment Handling"
msgstr "Ravnanje z naložbami"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"gncsecurities\">\"Securities and Investments\"</link> "
"above."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"gncsecurities\">\"Vrednostni papirji in naložbe\"</"
"link> zgoraj."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Turn this off if you wish to use the native method for future online price "
"quotes. See <link linkend=\"details.impexp.gncquotes\">\"Online Quotes\"</"
"link> above for more details."
msgstr ""
"To možnost izklopite, če želite za prihodnje spletne kotacije cen uporabiti "
"izvorno metodo. Glejte <link linkend=\"details.impexp.gncquotes\">\"Spletne "
"kotacije\"</link> zgoraj za več podrobnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"gncschedules\">\"Scheduled Transactions\"</link> above."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"gncschedules\">\"Načrtovane transakcije\"</link> "
"zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decoding Options"
msgstr "Možnosti dekodiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your native language is written in letters or symbols which are different "
"from those used in the 'Latin' languages (&ie;, generally Western European,) "
"these are represented in a special fashion (<quote>encoded</quote>) in your "
"&gnucash; file. If these characters are not displayed correctly on your "
"screen, then they must be decoded. Currently, it is often not possible to "
"detect accurately which form of decoding must be used, so you may need to "
"set this option manually by selecting an entry from the list. In general, "
"the first item in the list will be that which is considered appropriate for "
"your locale (&ie;, the country and language which was selected as native "
"when your operating system was installed,) so this should be tried first. "
"Since the import process does not overwrite your &gnucash; file, you are "
"free to experiment with any of these selections."
msgstr ""
"Če je vaš materni jezik napisan s črkami ali simboli, ki se razlikujejo od "
"tistih, ki se uporabljajo v 'latiničnih' jezikih (&ie; na splošno "
"zahodnoevropskih), so ti predstavljeni na poseben način (<quote>kodirani</"
"quote>) v vaši datoteki &gnucash;. Če ti znaki na zaslonu niso pravilno "
"prikazani, jih je treba dekodirati. Trenutno pogosto ni mogoče natančno "
"ugotoviti, katero obliko dekodiranja je treba uporabiti, zato boste morda "
"morali to možnost nastaviti ročno, tako da izberete vnos s seznama. Na "
"splošno bo prva postavka na seznamu tista, ki velja za primerno za vaše "
"lokalne nastavitve (&ie; država in jezik, ki sta bila izbrana kot izvorna, "
"ko je bil nameščen vaš operacijski sistem), zato morate to najprej "
"poskusiti. Ker postopek uvoza ne prepiše vaše datoteke &gnucash;, lahko "
"eksperimentirate s katero koli od teh izbir."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transaction Notes option"
msgstr "Možnost transakcijskih opomb"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Under some usage conditions, non-split &gnucash; transactions may contain "
"residual, often incorrect, memo data which is not normally visible to the "
"user. When imported into &kmymoney; however, due to display differences, "
"this data can become visible. Often, these transactions will have a Notes "
"field describing the real purpose of the transaction. If this option is "
"selected, these notes, if present, will be used to override the extraneous "
"memo data."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih pogojih uporabe nerazdeljeni &gnucash; transakcije lahko "
"vsebujejo ostanke, pogosto nepravilne podatke opomb, ki običajno niso vidni "
"uporabniku. Pri uvozu v &kmymoney; vendar lahko zaradi razlik v prikazu ti "
"podatki postanejo vidni. Pogosto imajo te transakcije polje z opombami, ki "
"opisuje pravi namen transakcije. Če je ta možnost izbrana, bodo te opombe, "
"če so prisotne, uporabljene za preglasitev tujih podatkov opomb."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Debug Options"
msgstr "Možnosti odpravljanja napak"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These need only be used in the event of import problems. If you have such "
"problems, you should also report them to the developers' mailing list "
"&devlist;. Note that the traces produced by these options may contain data "
"of a confidential nature, and the <guilabel>Anonymize data</guilabel> option "
"should be used if they are to be made publicly available."
msgstr ""
"Te je treba uporabiti samo v primeru težav z uvozom. Če imate takšne težave, "
"jih prijavite tudi na poštni seznam razvijalcev &devlist;. Upoštevajte, da "
"lahko sledi, ki jih ustvarijo te možnosti, vsebujejo podatke zaupne narave, "
"zato morate uporabiti možnost <guilabel>Anonimiziraj podatke</guilabel>, če "
"želite, da so javno dostopni."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import Report"
msgstr "Poročilo o uvozu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the end of processing, the importer produces a report showing the number "
"of different entities processed, and any errors or anomalies encountered. "
"This report will be displayed on screen, and may be saved to a file for "
"later review. A full report may contain the following sections:"
msgstr ""
"Na koncu obdelave uvoznik izdela poročilo, v katerem je prikazano število "
"različnih obdelanih entitet in morebitne napake ali anomalije, na katere je "
"naletel. To poročilo bo prikazano na zaslonu in se lahko shrani v datoteko "
"za poznejši pregled. Celotno poročilo lahko vsebuje naslednje razdelke:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Record counts"
msgstr "Štetje zapisov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inconsistencies in account types and actions taken"
msgstr "Nedoslednosti v vrstah računov in izvedenih ukrepih"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details of suspect schedules"
msgstr "Podrobnosti o sumljivih časovnih planih"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>gnucash importer report</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>poročilo uvoznika gnucash</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>gnucash importer report</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>poročilo uvoznika gnucash</phrase>"

#. Tag: author
#: details-impexp.docbook:489 details-impexp.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Thomas.Baumgart; &Thomas.Baumgart.mail;"
msgstr "&Thomas.Baumgart; &Thomas.Baumgart.mail;"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "QIF Importer"
msgstr "Uvoznik QIF"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "QIF format considered harmful"
msgstr "Format QIF velja za škodljivega"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Generally speaking, the QIF format should be avoided wherever possible. For "
"many reasons, it is a poor choice for transporting financial data. Among "
"other things, QIF suffers from these problems:"
msgstr ""
"Na splošno se je formatu QIF treba izogibati, kjer koli je to mogoče. Iz več "
"razlogov je slaba izbira za prenos finančnih podatkov. Med drugim QIF trpi "
"zaradi naslednjih težav:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lack of standardized format: Different versions of the same program will "
"impart different meanings to the same element."
msgstr ""
"Pomanjkanje standardiziranega formata: različne različice istega programa "
"bodo istemu elementu dale različne pomene."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lack of transaction identifier: Because there is no ID number associated "
"with each transaction, matching duplicate transactions is haphazard at best."
msgstr ""
"Pomanjkanje identifikatorja transakcije: Ker ni ID številke, povezane z "
"vsako transakcijo, je ujemanje podvojenih transakcij v najboljšem primeru "
"naključno."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lack of expressiveness: The grammar is really simple, and cannot portray the "
"depth of financial information found in today's financial environment."
msgstr ""
"Pomanjkanje izraznosti: Slovnica je zelo preprosta in ne more opisati "
"globine finančnih informacij v današnjem finančnem okolju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is generally why Intuit stopped supporting QIF input at all with "
"<application>Quicken</application> 2005. If you have the option of getting "
"data some other way, like OFX, always choose that option."
msgstr ""
"To je na splošno razlog, zakaj je Intuit sploh prenehal podpirati vnos QIF z "
"aplikacijo <application>Quicken</application> 2005. Če imate možnost "
"pridobivanja podatkov na drug način, na primer OFX, vedno izberite to "
"možnost."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to import a QIF file"
msgstr "Kako uvoziti datoteko QIF"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To import a QIF file, first ensure you have a valid &kmymoney; file open, "
"then select the <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>QIF...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uvoziti datoteko QIF, najprej zagotovite, da imate odrto veljavno "
"datoteko &kmymoney;, nato izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Uvoz</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>QIF..."
"</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>qif importer</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>uvoznik qif</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>qif importer</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>uvoznik qif</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The resulting dialog prompts for the QIF filename, allowing you to type in "
"the full path to the file or to locate the file by clicking "
"<guibutton>Browse</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Odprto pogovorno okno zahteva ime datoteke QIF, kar vam omogoča, da vnesete "
"celotno pot do datoteke ali poiščete datoteko s klikom na "
"<guibutton>Prebrskaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that &kmymoney; differentiates between the import of a bank statement "
"file and a file with historic data exported from another application. A bank "
"statement file does not necessarily include all the data related to a single "
"bank statement; it may contain only one or a few transactions. The default "
"is to import a bank statement file. In case you are importing data from your "
"previous personal finance manager application, select the appropriate option."
msgstr ""
"Tudi &kmymoney; razlikuje med uvozom datoteke bančnih izpiskov in "
"zgodovinskimi podatki, izvoženimi iz druge aplikacije. Privzeto je uvoz "
"datoteke bančnega izpiska. V primeru, da uvažate podatke iz vaše prejšnje "
"aplikacije za upravljanje osebnih financ, izberite ustrezno možnost."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, you need to select a QIF Profile for the import. Because there is no "
"universally standard format for a QIF file, different vendors have taken "
"liberties with the format, and introduced their own nuances. The QIF Profile "
"allows &kmymoney; to know about the peculiarities of your file. In general, "
"the default QIF profile should work with most QIF files. In some cases it "
"might be necessary to use a modified QIF profile. See the <link linkend="
"\"details.impexp.qif.profile\"> next section</link> for more details on that "
"subject."
msgstr ""
"Nato morate za uvoz izbrati profil QIF. Ker ni univerzalnega standardnega "
"formata za datoteko QIF, so si različni prodajalci vzeli svobodo glede "
"formata in uvedli svoje nianse. Profil QIF omogoča &kmymoney; vedeti o "
"posebnostih vaše datoteke. Na splošno bi moral privzeti profil QIF delovati "
"z večino datotek QIF. V nekaterih primerih bo morda treba uporabiti "
"spremenjen profil QIF. Oglejte si <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qif.profile"
"\"> naslednji razdelek</link> za več podrobnosti o tej temi."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guibutton>Import</guibutton> to import the QIF file."
msgstr "Kliknite <guibutton>Uvozi</guibutton>, da uvozite datoteko QIF."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; will start scanning the file to determine the formats used to "
"represent dates and numbers. In case it cannot determine a date format "
"unambiguously, &kmymoney; will ask the user to select one from the list of "
"possible date formats."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; bo začel prečesavati datoteko, da bi določil formate, uporabljene "
"za predstavitev datumov in števil. V primeru, da ne more nedvoumno določiti "
"formata datuma, bo &kmymoney; od uporabnika zahteval, da izbere enega od "
"možnih formatov datuma iz seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, &kmymoney; imports the data and creates all necessary objects, such as "
"payee information, account and category records, and stock price "
"information. Wherever possible, existing transactions will be matched "
"against the imported information, to avoid duplicate transactions. A "
"progress bar is shown and updated during the import process."
msgstr ""
"Nato &kmymoney; uvozi podatke in ustvari vse potrebne objekte, kot so "
"informacije o prejemniku plačila, zapisi računov in kategorij ter "
"informacije o tečajih delnic. Kadar koli je to mogoče, bodo obstoječe "
"transakcije primerjane z uvoženimi informacijami, da se prepreči podvojene "
"transakcije. Med postopkom uvoza je prikazana in posodobljena vrstica "
"napredka."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case &kmymoney; could not detect the name of the account to be imported, "
"the user will be asked to select the account into which the data should be "
"imported. If the account does not already exist in your file, a new account "
"can be created by clicking <guibutton>Create</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"V primeru, da &kmymoney; ni mogel zaznati imena računa za uvoz, bo uporabnik "
"pozvan, da izbere račun, v katerega naj se podatki uvozijo. Če račun še ne "
"obstaja v vaši datoteki, lahko ustvarite nov račun s klikom na "
"<guibutton>Ustvari</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the end of the import, &kmymoney; shows a statement import statistics "
"window."
msgstr "Na koncu uvoza se &kmymoney; prikaže okno statistike uvoza izpiskov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>qif import statement statistics</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>statistika uvoznih zapisov qif</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>qif import statement statistics</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>statistika uvoznih zapisov qif</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After importing, all of the imported transactions will be shown with a "
"yellow background in the Ledgers View. In case &kmymoney; was able to match "
"an imported transaction with an already existing transaction, the background "
"is shown in light green."
msgstr ""
"Po uvozu bodo vse uvožene transakcije prikazane z rumenim ozadjem v Pogledu "
"glavne knjige. V primeru, da je &kmymoney; uspelo ujeti  uvoženo transakcijo "
"z že obstoječo transakcijo, je ozadje prikazano v svetlo zeleni barvi."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The colors used to mark imported and matched transactions are customizable "
"and may be different in your environment."
msgstr ""
"Barve, ki se uporabljajo za označevanje uvoženih in ujemajočih se "
"transakcij, so prilagodljive in se lahko razlikujejo v vašem okolju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next step is to verify the imported data and accept all the imported "
"transactions. This is a general process and also applies to imports from "
"other sources. It is similar to the process for <link linkend=\"details."
"ledgers.match\">matched transactions</link>. All imported transactions are "
"marked in the ledger with an <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"icon-imported.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>imported icon. Once you <quote>Accept</quote> the "
"transaction, it is no longer marked as Imported."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji korak je preverjanje uvoženih podatkov in sprejem vseh uvoženih "
"transakcij. To je splošen postopek in velja tudi za uvoze iz drugih virov. "
"Podoben je postopku za <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.match\">ujemajoče se "
"transakcije</link>. Vse uvožene transakcije so v knjigi označene z ikono "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-imported.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>uvoženo. Ko transakcijo "
"<quote>Sprejme</quote>, ni več označena kot uvožena."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transaction matching"
msgstr "Ujemanje transakcij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As noted previously, one of the major drawbacks of the QIF format is the "
"lack of a unique identifier for each transaction. Thus, if you import a QIF "
"file and some of the transactions are already in your ledger, you may get "
"duplicates. &kmymoney; attempts to get around this by looking for "
"transactions that look similar to those you already have. If it finds "
"something that looks like the same transaction, it will match the apparent "
"duplicate."
msgstr ""
"Kot smo že omenili, je ena glavnih pomanjkljivosti formata QIF pomanjkanje "
"edinstvenega identifikatorja za vsako transakcijo. Če torej uvozite datoteko "
"QIF in so nekatere transakcije že v vaši glavni knjigi, lahko dobite "
"dvojnike. &kmymoney; poskuša te problem zaobiti tako, da išče transakcije, "
"ki so videti podobne tistim, ki jih že imate. Če najde nekaj, kar je videti "
"kot ista transakcija, se bo ujemalo z navideznim dvojnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This can be a problem if you have transactions that look very similar but "
"are actually different. In this case, you can unmatch those transactions "
"later in the Ledger View."
msgstr ""
"To je lahko težava, če imate transakcije, ki so videti zelo podobne, vendar "
"so v resnici različne. V tem primeru lahko te transakcije kasneje "
"razveljavite v pogledu glavne knjige."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "Writing an import filter"
msgstr "Pisanje uvoznega filtra"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you may have data in a custom format, like comma-separated-values "
"(CSV) or something else unique to your situation. As of version 4.6, "
"&kmymoney; includes a CSV Importer Plugin, but you can still import other "
"types of files into &kmymoney; using a QIF Import Filter. A filter is a "
"custom program you write which takes your special file as input, and "
"produces a QIF file as output. This can be a shell script, a perl script, a "
"compiled program written in C/C++, or anything else you can dream of, as "
"long as the system can run it. The filter will be run with the input file as "
"stdin and stdout is assumed to be a valid qif file to pass on to the actual "
"QIF importer."
msgstr ""
"Včasih imate morda podatke v obliki po meri, kot so vrednosti, ločene z "
"vejicami (CSV) ali kaj drugega, kar je edinstveno za vašo situacijo. Od "
"različice 4.6 naprej &kmymoney; vključuje vtičnik za uvoz CSV, vendar lahko "
"še vedno lahko uvozite druge vrste datotek v &kmymoney; z uporabo uvoznega "
"filtra QIF. Filter je program po meri, ki ga napišete in vzame vašo posebno "
"datoteko kot vhod in ustvari datoteko QIF kot izhod. To je lahko lupinski "
"skript, perl skript, preveden program napisan v C/C++, ali karkoli drugega, "
"o čemer lahko sanjate, če ga le sistem lahko izvaja."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use a filter, edit your favorite QIF Profile or create a new one (see the "
"next section for details on QIF Profiles,) and select the Filter tab. Enter "
"the full path to your filter program in the <guilabel>Input filter location</"
"guilabel> field, or click the browse icon next to the field and navigate to "
"the filter in the <guilabel>File Open...</guilabel> dialog. Then, whenever "
"you do a QIF import using this profile, the file you select for importing "
"will be run through your filter first. Note that the filter location field "
"contains the full path to the filter program or script, but can also include "
"command line parameters for the program."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti filter, uredite svoj najljubši profil QIF ali ustvarite "
"novega (za podrobnosti o profilih QIF glejte naslednji razdelek) in izberite "
"zavihek Filter. V polje <guilabel>Lokacija vnosnega filtra</guilabel> "
"vnesite celotno pot do vašega filtrirnega programa ali kliknite ikono za "
"brskanje poleg polja in se pomaknite do filtra v pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Odpri datoteko...</guilabel>. Nato, kadar koli uvozite QIF s tem "
"profilom, bo datoteka, ki jo izberete za uvoz, najprej prešla skozi vaš "
"filter. Upoštevajte, da polje lokacije filtra vsebuje celotno pot do "
"filtrirnega programa ali skripta, in lahko vključuje tudi parametre ukazne "
"vrstice za program."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, if you want the <guilabel>File Open...</guilabel> dialog where you "
"choose the file to input to have a filter for your specific file type, enter "
"a comma separated list of file filters (such as <quote>*.abc,*.xyz</quote>) "
"in the <guilabel>Input filter file type</guilabel> field. With the above "
"example, when you open a file for import using this profile, you will only "
"see files ending in abc or xyz. If you leave the field empty, no name "
"filtering will be done, and you will see all files."
msgstr ""
"Nato, če želite, da ima pogovorno okno <guilabel>Odpiranje datoteke...</"
"guilabel>, kjer izberete datoteko za vnos, filter za vašo določeno vrsto "
"datoteke, vnesite seznam filtrov datotek, ločenih z vejicami (kot je <quote> "
"*.abc,*.xyz</quote>) v polju <guilabel>Vrsta datoteke vhodnega filtra</"
"guilabel>. V zgornjem primeru, ko odprete datoteko za uvoz s tem profilom, "
"boste videli samo datoteke, ki se končajo z abc ali xyz. Če pustite polje "
"prazno, filtriranje imen ne bo izvedeno in videli boste vse datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A common problem is to convert a list of comma-separated-values into a QIF "
"file. Prior to the addition of &kmymoney;'s CSV Importer plugin, this would "
"have been a textbook case for the <command>awk</command> tool. We still use "
"this example here, just to show a sample of how the import filter process "
"works. Create a script called <filename>csv2qif.awk</filename>, with the "
"following two lines as contents:"
msgstr ""
"Pogosta težava je pretvorba seznama vrednosti, ločenih z vejicami, v "
"datoteko QIF. Pred dodajanjem vtičnika za uvoz CSV &kmymoney; je bil to "
"učbeniški primer za orodje <command>awk</command>. Tukaj še vedno "
"uporabljamo ta primer samo za prikaz vzorca delovanja postopka uvoznega "
"filtra. Ustvarite skript z imenom <filename>csv2qif.awk</filename> z "
"naslednjima dvema vrsticama kot vsebino:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: details-impexp.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"BEGIN { FS=&quot;,&quot;; print &quot;!Type:Bank&quot; }\n"
"\n"
"    { print &quot;D&quot;$1; print &quot;T&quot;$2; print &quot;N&quot;$3; "
"print &quot;P&quot;$4; print &quot;M&quot;$5; print &quot;^&quot; }"
msgstr ""
"BEGIN { FS=&quot;,&quot;; print &quot;!Type:Bank&quot; }\n"
"\n"
"    { print &quot;D&quot;$1; print &quot;T&quot;$2; print &quot;N&quot;$3; "
"print &quot;P&quot;$4; print &quot;M&quot;$5; print &quot;^&quot; }"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then, change the QIF keys (D,T,N,P,M) to match the order of the columns in "
"your CSV data. Set the input filter to <userinput>awk -f csv2qif.awk</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nato spremenite ključe QIF (D,T,N,P,M), da bodo ustrezali vrstnemu redu "
"vaših podatkov CSV. Vhodni filter nastavite na <userinput>awk -f csv2qif."
"awk</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another problem sometimes arises in the encoding of QIF files. &kmymoney; "
"expects files to be UTF8 encoded. If your file is encoded in something else, "
"it can be useful to convert it to UTF8. For example to convert it from "
"iso-8859-1, you would set the input filter to <userinput>recode iso-8859-1.."
"utf-8</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Druga težava se včasih pojavi pri kodiranju datotek QIF. &kmymoney; "
"pričakuje, da bodo datoteke kodirane z UTF8. Če je vaša datoteka kodirana v "
"nečem drugem, jo je lahko koristno pretvoriti v UTF8. Če ga želite na primer "
"pretvoriti iz iso-8859-1, bi morali vhodni filter nastaviti na "
"<userinput>rekodiranje iso-8859-1..utf-8</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special &kmymoney; QIF extensions"
msgstr "Posebni &kmymoney; razširitve QIF"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As already mentioned, one of the major drawbacks of the QIF format is the "
"lack of a unique identifier for each transaction. If you are writing your "
"own QIF file creator (or filter, as described above,) you can overcome this "
"problem. &kmymoney; supports the '#' field. The importer will interpret this "
"as a unique transaction ID, and disregard the record if the transaction is "
"already in the system."
msgstr ""
"Kot že omenjeno, je ena glavnih pomanjkljivosti formata QIF pomanjkanje "
"edinstvenega identifikatorja za vsako transakcijo. Če pišete svoj lastni "
"ustvarjalec datotek QIF (ali filter, kot je opisano zgoraj), lahko premagate "
"to težavo. &kmymoney; podpira polje '#'. Uvoznik bo to interpretiral kot "
"edinstven ID transakcije in prezrl zapis, če je transakcija že v sistemu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "QIF Profiles"
msgstr "Profili QIF"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit an existing QIF Profile, or to create a new one, bring up the QIF "
"Importer dialog by selecting <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>,</keycap> </keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from the "
"main menu, clicking <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"preferences-plugin.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> at the bottom of the left "
"panel, and clicking &configicon; Configure on the entry for <quote>QIF "
"Importer</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti obstoječi profil QIF ali ustvariti novega, odprite "
"pogovorno okno uvoznika QIF tako, da izberete <menuchoice> <shortcut> "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>,</keycap> </keycombo> </shortcut > "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmymoney;...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju in kliknite <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"preferences-plugin.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> "
"</imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel> na dnu "
"leve plošče in kliknite &configicon; Konfiguriraj vnos za <quote>Uvoznik "
"QIF</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that because the QIF Importer and the QIF Exporter are implemented as "
"separate plugins, there are separate entries for each on the Plugins "
"configuration dialog. Configuring either one brings up the same Profile "
"Editor dialog."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da ker sta uvoznik QIF in izvoznik QIF implementirana kot "
"ločena vtičnika, sta za vsakega ločena vnosa v pogovornem oknu za "
"konfiguracijo vtičnikov. Če konfigurirate enega ali drugega, se prikaže isto "
"pogovorno okno urejevalnika profilov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>qif profile editor general tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>splošen zavihek urejevalnika profilov qif</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>qif profile editor general tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>splošen zavihek urejevalnika profilov qif</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left, the Profile selector displays a list of all existing QIF "
"Profiles; select one to edit its configuration. To create a new profile, "
"press the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button. You can rename an existing "
"profile by selecting it in the Profile selector and clicking "
"<guibutton>Rename</guibutton>, and delete one with the <guibutton>Delete</"
"guibutton> button. Clicking <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> resets all the "
"fields of the currently displayed profile to their default values."
msgstr ""
"Na levi izbirnik profila prikaže seznam vseh obstoječih profilov QIF; "
"izberite enega, da uredite njegovo konfiguracijo. Če želite ustvariti nov "
"profil, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Nov</guibutton>. Obstoječi profil lahko "
"preimenujete tako, da ga izberete v izbirniku profila in kliknete "
"<guibutton>Preimenuj</guibutton>, enega pa izbrišete z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton>. Če kliknete <guibutton>Ponastavi</"
"guibutton>, se vsa polja trenutno prikazanega profila ponastavijo na "
"privzete vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "The right area of the dialog has four tabs."
msgstr "Desno območje pogovornega okna ima štiri zavihke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>General</quote> tab contains a field for a description of the "
"filter, several fields to specify what &kmymoney; should expect certain "
"fields to look like in the qif file output by the filter, and a checkbox "
"which tells &kmymoney; whether or not to attempt to match similar "
"transactions to avoid duplicates."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <quote>Splošno</quote> vsebuje polje za opis filtra, več polj za "
"določitev, kaj &kmymoney; bi morali pričakovati, da bodo nekatera polja "
"videti kot v izpisu datoteke qif filtra, in potrditveno polje, ki pove "
"&kmymoney; ali naj poskusi ujemati podobne transakcije ali ne, da se izogne ​​"
"dvojnikom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>qif profile editor filter tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>zavihek filtra urejevalnika profila qif</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>qif profile editor filter tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>zavihek filtra urejevalnika profila qif</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Filter</quote> tab allows you to specify the location of both an "
"import filter, as described in the <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qif.filter"
"\">previous section</link> as well as an output filter, which works "
"similarly, but is applied when writing out a data file. The <guilabel>Input "
"filter file type</guilabel> is not applicable to an output filter, as the "
"file dialog for the file to be written does not require filtering."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <quote>Filter</quote> vam omogoča, da določite lokacijo uvoznega "
"filtra, kot je opisano v <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qif.filter"
"\">prejšnjem razdelku</link>, kot tudi izhodni filter, ki deluje podobno, "
"vendar se uporablja pri zapisovanju podatkovne datoteke. <guilabel>Vrsta "
"datoteke vhodnega filtra</guilabel> ni uporabna za izhodni filter, saj "
"pogovorno okno datoteke za zapisovanje datoteke ne zahteva filtriranja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>qif profile editor date tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>zavihek z urejevalnikom datuma profila qif</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>qif profile editor date tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>zavihek z urejevalnikom datuma profila qif</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:805
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Date</quote> tab is primarily applicable to QIF Export, as "
"&kmymoney; is usually able to determine the date format by examining the "
"actual data. The primary purpose is to specify the order of the date parts, "
"and the delimiter which separates them."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <quote>Datum</quote> se uporablja predvsem za izvoz QIF, ker lahko "
"&kmymoney; običajno določi obliko datuma s pregledom dejanskih podatkov. "
"Primarni namen je določiti vrstni red delov datuma in ločilo, ki jih ločuje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because the QIF format is not standardized, it's impossible to know which "
"century is meant when using two digit years. In QIF files with two digit "
"years, there is an assumed default century, and an apostrophe is used as the "
"year separator to specify that entry is in the OTHER century. However, since "
"which century is assumed to be the default is not standardized, the "
"<guilabel>Apostrophe Handling</guilabel> field is used for this purpose, "
"indicating the intended century when an apostrophe is used as the year "
"separator. As an example, you would set the Apostrophe Format to "
"&quot;2000-2099&quot;, so dates with an apostrophe will be interpreted as "
"being &gt; year 2000. In this case, dates without an apostrophe will be "
"treated as being in the 1900's."
msgstr ""
"Ker format QIF ni standardiziran, je nemogoče vedeti, katero stoletje je "
"mišljeno pri uporabi dvomestnih letnic. V datotekah QIF z dvomestno letnico "
"je predpostavljeno privzeto stoletje, apostrof pa se uporablja kot ločilo "
"let, da se določi, da je vnos v DRUGEM stoletju. Ker pa se domneva, da je "
"privzeto stoletje, ni standardizirano, se za ta namen uporabi polje "
"<guilabel>Ravnanje z apostrofom</guilabel>, ki označuje predvideno stoletje, "
"ko se kot ločilo let uporablja apostrof. Na primer, format apostrofa bi "
"nastavili na &quot;2000-2099&quot;, tako da bodo datumi z apostrofom "
"interpretirani kot &gt; leta 2000. V tem primeru bodo datumi brez apostrofa "
"obravnavani kot leta od 1900 naprej."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>qif profile editor amounts tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>zavihek urejevalnika zneskov profila qif</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>qif profile editor amounts tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>zavihek urejevalnika zneskov profila qif</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Amounts</quote> tab is used on QIF Export to specify the Decimal "
"Symbol and Thousands Separator to be used. However, you need to specify "
"those for each line in the QIF file which can contain an amount. To alter "
"those settings, click one of the lines in the upper part of the display, "
"then use the dropdowns below to set the characters to be used."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <quote>Zneski</quote> se uporablja pri izvozu QIF za določitev "
"decimalnega simbola in ločila tisočic, ki naj se uporabita. Vendar jih "
"morate določiti za vsako vrstico v datoteki QIF, ki lahko vsebuje znesek. Če "
"želite spremeniti te nastavitve, kliknite eno od vrstic v zgornjem delu "
"zaslona, ​​nato pa uporabite spodnje spustne menije, da nastavite znake, ki "
"jih želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid "QIF Exporter"
msgstr "Izvoznik QIF"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export one of your accounts to a QIF file, choose the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Export</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>QIF...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. You will be prompted for which single "
"account to export, what file to export it to, and what QIF Profile to use."
msgstr ""
"Če želite enega od svojih računov izvoziti v datoteko QIF, izberite menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izvozi</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>QIF...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Pozvani boste, "
"kateri posamezni račun želite izvoziti, v katero datoteko izvoziti in kateri "
"profil QIF uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The QIF Exporter does not handle export of investment accounts. It may "
"appear to work, and will produce an output file, but that file will not "
"include any actual data."
msgstr ""
"Izvoznik QIF ne upravlja izvoza naložbenih računov. Morda se zdi, da deluje, "
"in bo ustvaril izhodno datoteko, vendar ta datoteka ne bo vključevala "
"nobenih dejanskih podatkov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>qif exporter</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>izvoznik qif</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>qif exporter</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>izvoznik qif</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The QIF Exporter uses QIF Profiles in a similar way as the QIF Importer, but "
"it uses the information in the Profile to format the QIF file being written, "
"rather than to interpret the file being read. Parallel to the importer, you "
"can use a custom written filter program. There is a separate field on the "
"Filter Tab of the QIF Profile editor for an output filter, so you can use "
"the same QIF Profile for both importing and exporting, but use a separate "
"filter for the two processes."
msgstr ""
"Izvoznik QIF uporablja profile QIF na podoben način kot uvoznik QIF, vendar "
"uporablja informacije v profilu za formatiranje datoteke QIF, ki se piše, "
"namesto za interpretacijo datoteke, ki se bere. Vzporedno z uvoznikom lahko "
"uporabite po meri napisan filtrirni program. Na zavihku Filter urejevalnika "
"profila QIF je ločeno polje za izhodni filter, tako da lahko uporabite isti "
"profil QIF za uvoz in izvoz, vendar uporabite ločen filter za oba procesa."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid "OFX Importer"
msgstr "Uvoznik QIF"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The OFX importer was one of the first components of &kmymoney; to be written "
"as a Plugin. At that time, there were only a few plugins included in the "
"source code, and they were not always included in versions built for &Linux; "
"distributions, so it was sometimes necessary for users to be able to compile "
"the plugins themselves. This is rarely the case any more, but see the "
"section on <link linkend=\"makingmostof.plugins\">Plugins</link> for more "
"information. Currently, many of the features considered core parts of "
"&kmymoney; are implemented as plugins, so that fact is not always mentioned "
"in this handbook where those features are discussed. See also the <link "
"linkend=\"details.settings.plugins\">Plugins</link> section in the Settings "
"Chapter."
msgstr ""
"Uvoznik OFX je bil ena od prvih komponent &kmymoney; napisan kot vtičnik. "
"Takrat je bilo v izvorno kodo vključenih le nekaj vtičnikov in niso bili "
"vedno vključeni v različice, izdelane za distribucije &Linux;, zato je bilo "
"včasih potrebno, da so lahko uporabniki sami prevedli vtičnike. To se zdaj "
"le redkokdaj dogaja, vendar si za več informacij oglejte razdelek o <link "
"linkend=\"makingmostof.plugins\">Vtičnikih</link>. Trenutno je veliko "
"funkcij, ki veljajo za jedrne dele &kmymoney;, ki so implementirani kot "
"vtičniki, tako da to dejstvo ni vedno omenjeno v tem priročniku, kjer se "
"obravnavajo te funkcije. Glejte tudi razdelek <link linkend=\"details."
"settings.plugins\">Vtičniki</link> v poglavju o nastavitvah."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:904
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is OFX"
msgstr "Kaj je OFX"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>OFX</acronym> stands for <quote>Open Financial Exchange</quote>. "
"According to the <ulink url=\"https://financialdataexchange.org/ofx/\">OFX "
"Work Group web site</ulink> <quote>Open Financial Exchange is an open "
"standard for client-server systems and cloud based APIs for exchanging "
"financial data, and performing financial transactions between financial "
"institutions, and financial applications.</quote> The specification defines "
"formats for transfer of financial data both by file and by direct "
"interchange. Additional historic information may be found on the <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_Financial_Exchange\">Wikipedia page</"
"ulink>"
msgstr ""
"<acronym>OFX</acronym> pomeni <quote>Open Financial Exchange - Odprta "
"finančna izmenjava</quote>. Glede na <ulink url=\"https://"
"financialdataexchange.org/ofx/\">spletno mesto OFX Work Group</ulink> "
"<quote>Open Financial Exchange je odprt standard za sisteme odjemalec-"
"strežnik in API-je v oblaku za izmenjavo finančni podatkov in izvajanje "
"finančnih transakcij med finančnimi institucijami in finančnimi aplikacijami."
"</quote> Specifikacija določa formate za prenos finančnih podatkov tako z "
"datoteko kot z neposredno izmenjavo. Dodatne zgodovinske informacije najdete "
"na <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_Financial_Exchange"
"\">strani Wikipedije</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although the OFX standard is much more complete and robust than QIF, there "
"are still variations, depending on the specific implementation used by any "
"institution. OFX files may have an extension of <quote>OFX</quote> or "
"<quote>QFX</quote> (upper or lower case); this does not imply any particular "
"difference in the content. The specification was originally based on SGML, "
"and more recent versions are based on &XML;, so the files can be read in any "
"text editor, but as whitespace is not relevant to the content itself, some "
"implementations do not use any, making it very hard for a human to read."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je standard OFX veliko popolnejši in robustnejši od QIF, še vedno "
"obstajajo različice, odvisno od specifične implementacije, ki jo uporablja "
"katera koli institucija. Datoteke OFX imajo lahko končnico <quote>OFX</"
"quote> ali <quote>QFX</quote> (velike ali male črke); to ne pomeni nobene "
"posebne vsebinske razlike. Specifikacija je prvotno temeljila na SGML, "
"novejše različice pa temeljijo na &XML;, tako da je datoteke mogoče brati v "
"katerem koli urejevalniku besedila, a ker presledek ni pomemben za samo "
"vsebino, ga nekatere izvedbe ne uporabljajo, zaradi česar to človek zelo "
"težko bere."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition, even though the standard includes provisions for additional "
"types of data, &kmymoney; is only able to import transaction data, with some "
"additional data such as the current balance of accounts."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega, čeprav standard vključuje določbe za dodatne vrste podatkov, "
"&kmymoney; lahko samo uvozi transakcijske podatke z nekaterimi dodatnimi "
"podatki, kot je trenutno stanje na računih."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although it appears to have disappeared, there used to be another site with "
"good information at <ulink url=\"https:/ofxhome.com/\">OFX Home</ulink>, "
"which maintained a directory of financial institutions that support OFX. "
"This was often useful if you had problems setting up <link linkend=\"details."
"impexp.ofxdirectconnect\">OFX direct connect.</link> They also had a forum "
"for discussions about OFX issues. As the domain is still registered, we will "
"leave this reference just in case the site reappears in the future."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav se zdi, da je izginilo, je nekoč obstajalo drugo spletno mesto z "
"dobrimi informacijami na naslovu <ulink url=\"https:/ofxhome.com/\">OFX "
"Home</ulink>, ki je vzdrževalo imenik finančnih ustanov, ki podpirajo OFX. "
"To je bilo pogosto uporabno, če ste imeli težave pri nastavljanju <link "
"linkend=\"details.impexp.ofxdirectconnect\"> neposredne povezave OFX.</link> "
"Imeli so tudi forum za razprave o vprašanjih OFX. Ker je domena še vedno "
"registrirana, bomo to referenco pustili za primer, če se spletno mesto v "
"prihodnosti ponovno pojavi."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:944
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing OFX data"
msgstr "Uvažanje podatkov OFX"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The OFX standard defines the organization and formatting of financial data, "
"but that data can exist either as a regular file or as a stream of data "
"between two computers. The most straightforward way of getting OFX data is "
"to download it from your bank or other financial institution as an OFX file. "
"In most cases, when you are logged into the bank's web site, on the page "
"which displays your transactions, there is a button or link for downloading "
"that data. It may say OFX or QFX, or you may request the data for Quicken or "
"Web Connect (see below for more on this term.) You also have the option of "
"specifying the date range of transactions to download (although that is "
"sometimes restricted to periods matching the available statements,) as well "
"as filtering by type of transaction."
msgstr ""
"Standard OFX določa organizacijo in oblikovanje finančnih podatkov, vendar "
"ti podatki lahko obstajajo kot navadna datoteka ali kot tok podatkov med "
"dvema računalnikoma. Najpreprostejši način pridobivanja podatkov OFX je, da "
"jih prenesete iz svoje banke ali druge finančne ustanove kot datoteko OFX. V "
"večini primerov, ko ste prijavljeni na spletno stran banke, je na strani, ki "
"prikazuje vaše transakcije, gumb ali povezava za prenos teh podatkov. Lahko "
"piše OFX ali QFX ali pa lahko zahtevate podatke za Quicken ali Web Connect "
"(glejte spodaj za več o tem izrazu). Prav tako imate možnost določiti "
"časovno obdobje transakcij za prenos (čeprav je to včasih omejeno na obdobja "
"ujemanje razpoložljivih izpiskov), kot tudi filtriranje po vrsti transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have downloaded an OFX file, the most basic way to import it is to "
"choose the importer from the menu bar, selecting the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>OFX...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. If OFX does not show up under Import, "
"you do not have the OFX Importer Plugin installed correctly, or it is not "
"enabled. Please see the previous section."
msgstr ""
"Če ste prenesli datoteko OFX, je najosnovnejši način uvoza tako, da v "
"menijski vrstici izberete uvoznik in izberete element menija <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Uvoz</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>OFX..."
"</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Če se OFX ne prikaže pod Uvoz, nimate pravilno "
"nameščenega vtičnika OFX Importer Plugin ali pa ni omogočen. Oglejte si "
"prejšnji razdelek."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first thing the importer will do is ask you into which account to import "
"the transactions. If the file includes transactions from multiple accounts, "
"you will be asked this question multiple times."
msgstr ""
"Prva stvar, ki jo bo uvoznik naredil, je, da vas bo vprašal, na kateri račun "
"naj uvozi transakcije. Če datoteka vključuje transakcije z več računov, bo "
"to vprašanje podal večkrat."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After importing, some of your transactions may be shown with an exclamation "
"mark on a yellow triangle in the ledger. This is because they need to be "
"assigned a category. The importer was not able to automatically assign a "
"category based on your past transaction history. You can edit each "
"transaction in the ledger to assign a category, and the mark will be removed."
msgstr ""
"Po uvozu so lahko nekatere vaše transakcije prikazane s klicajem na rumenem "
"trikotniku v glavni knjigi. To je zato, ker jim je treba dodeliti "
"kategorijo. Uvoznik ni mogel samodejno dodeliti kategorije na podlagi vaše "
"pretekle zgodovine transakcij. Vsako transakcijo v knjigi lahko uredite "
"tako, da ji dodelite kategorijo, in oznaka bo odstranjena."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section describes the <quote>native</quote> OFX importer. OFX files may "
"also be imported using the AqBanking Importer Plugin. The two importers do "
"behave slightly differently, and they are written and supported by two "
"different developers."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek opisuje <quote>izvorni</quote> uvoznik OFX. Datoteke OFX je "
"mogoče uvoziti tudi z vtičnikom AqBanking Importer Plugin. Oba uvoznika se "
"res obnašata nekoliko drugače, pišeta in podpirata ju dva različna "
"razvijalca."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Investments"
msgstr "Uvoz naložb"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:989
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that if you are importing a file with investment transactions, "
"those investments must first exist in your &kmymoney; file. The trading "
"symbol is used to match, so please ensure that the symbol in &kmymoney; is "
"exactly the same as the one in the file you're importing."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da če uvažate datoteko z naložbenimi transakcijami, morajo te "
"naložbe najprej obstajati v vaši mapi &kmymoney;. Trgovalni simbol se "
"uporablja za ujemanje, zato poskrbite, da simbol v &kmymoney; je popolnoma "
"enak tistemu v datoteki, ki jo uvažate."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:999
#, no-c-format
msgid "Web Connect"
msgstr "Spletna povezava"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rather than explicitly downloading an OFX file, as described above, an "
"easier way to import an OFX file is to set up Web Connect. Visit your bank's "
"web site, and click the button or link to download your data as an OFX file. "
"(Some institutions will only list QFX, which is equivalent.) Your browser "
"should ask whether you want to save the file, or else what program you would "
"like to use to open the file. Point your browser to &kmymoney;. It will then "
"import the downloaded OFX file directly into the &kmymoney; file you "
"currently have open, or the file you most recently had open. You can also "
"change the file associations of your desktop environment, and have the "
"system automatically open &kmymoney; if you click an OFX file in your file "
"browser."
msgstr ""
"Namesto izrecnega prenosa datoteke OFX, kot je opisano zgoraj, je lažji "
"način uvoza datoteke OFX nastavitev spletne povezave. Obiščite spletno mesto "
"svoje banke in kliknite gumb ali povezavo, da prenesete svoje podatke kot "
"datoteko OFX. (Nekatere institucije bodo navedle samo QFX, kar je "
"enakovredno.) Vaš brskalnik bi vas moral vprašati, ali želite shraniti "
"datoteko, ali kateri program želite uporabiti za odpiranje datoteke. "
"Pokažite svoj brskalnik na &kmymoney;. Nato bo preneseno datoteko OFX uvozil "
"neposredno v &kmymoney; datoteko, ki jo imate trenutno odprto, ali datoteko, "
"ki ste jo nazadnje odprli. Prav tako lahko spremenite povezave datotek "
"vašega namiznega okolja in sistem samodejno odpre &kmymoney; če kliknete "
"datoteko OFX v brskalniku datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to import the OFX file into some other &kmymoney; data file, "
"open that file in &kmymoney; first, and then visit your bank's web site."
msgstr ""
"Če morate datoteko OFX uvoziti v drugo podatkovno datoteko &kmymoney;, "
"odprite to datoteko v &kmymoney; in najprej obiščite spletno mesto svoje "
"banke."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:1019
#, no-c-format
msgid "Direct Connect"
msgstr "Neposredna povezava"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; also supports OFX Direct Connect. This gives &kmymoney; the "
"ability to contact your bank directly to download transactions, assuming the "
"bank supports it."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; podpira tudi OFX Direct Connect. To omogoča &kmymoney; možnost "
"neposrednega stika z vašo banko za prenos transakcij, če banka to podpira."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please be warned: not all banks support OFX Direct Connect, and those that "
"do often use software provided and supported by third parties, and those "
"third parties often provide customer support only to users of specific, "
"commercial financial management software. No bank directly supports "
"&kmymoney;, so you may have to tell them you want to bank directly from "
"<application>MS Money</application> or <application>Quicken</application>. "
"In addition, the OFX Work Group web site mentioned above also says "
"<quote>Further, the API allows the exchange to be facilitated either "
"directly or via an intermediary such as data aggregation service providers.</"
"quote> Users have reported that banks which have migrated to using such "
"aggregation service providers are even less likely to provide any support "
"unless you are using one of the commercial applications."
msgstr ""
"Opozorilo: vse banke ne podpirajo OFX Direct Connect in tiste to podpirajo "
"pogosto uporabljajo programsko opremo, ki jo nudijo in podpirajo tretje "
"osebe, in te tretje osebe pogosto nudijo podporo strankam samo uporabnikom "
"posebne komercialne programske opreme za finančno upravljanje. Nobena banka "
"neposredno ne podpira &kmymoney;, zato ji boste morda morali povedati, da "
"želite bančništvo neposredno iz <application>MS Money</application> ali "
"<application>Quicken</application>. Poleg tega zgoraj omenjeno spletno mesto "
"OFX Work Group prav tako pravi <quote>Poleg tega API omogoča olajšanje "
"izmenjave neposredno ali prek posrednika, kot so ponudniki storitev "
"združevanja podatkov.</quote> Uporabniki so poročali, da je za banke, ki so "
"prešle na uporabo takšnih ponudnikov storitev združevanja še manj verjetno, "
"da bodo zagotovile kakršno koli podporo, razen če uporabljate eno od "
"komercialnih aplikacij."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition, your bank may require a separate signup than for the regular "
"web site, it may give you a separate password or PIN, and it may even charge "
"you a separate fee for this service."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko vaša banka zahteva ločeno prijavo kot za običajno spletno "
"stran, lahko vam da ločeno geslo ali PIN in vam lahko celo zaračuna ločeno "
"pristojbino za to storitev."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If Direct Connect works for you, it allows you to update your records by "
"downloading recent transactions with a single button push. If it does not "
"work on your first attempt, you may find an easy solution to your issue, or "
"it may take a lot of research, and there is no guarantee that it will work "
"in any particular situation. However, please do not take any of this as a "
"reason to not try it."
msgstr ""
"Če Direct Connect deluje pri vas, vam omogoča posodobitev vaših zapisov s "
"prenosom nedavnih transakcij z enim samim pritiskom na gumb. Če ne deluje ob "
"prvem poskusu, boste morda našli enostavno rešitev za vašo težavo ali pa "
"boste morda potrebovali veliko raziskav in ni nobenega zagotovila, da bo "
"delovalo v določeni situaciji. Vendar prosim, ničesar od tega ne jemljite "
"kot razlog, da tega ne poskusite."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step is to configure each account for which you wish to download "
"transactions. Go to the Accounts view, right-click the account you wish to "
"configure, and choose <guimenuitem>Map to online account...</guimenuitem>. "
"This is also available from the <guimenu>Accounts</guimenu> menu if the "
"account is open in the Ledgers View. In case more than one online banking "
"plugin is installed on your system you will be asked which one to use. For "
"the internal OFX method select <guimenuitem>&kmymoney; OFX</guimenuitem>. A "
"list of banks will be downloaded from the Internet and a wizard will guide "
"you through choosing a bank, entering your username and password, and "
"selecting an account. Should you find that your bank is not listed, then it "
"may still be possible to use the manual option. Your bank may be able to "
"provide the required parameters, or you may have to do some research to find "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak je konfiguracija vsakega računa, za katerega želite prenesti "
"transakcije. Pojdite v pogled Računi, z desno miškino tipko kliknite račun, "
"ki ga želite konfigurirati, in izberite <guimenuitem>Preslikaj v spletni "
"račun...</guimenuitem>. To je na voljo tudi v meniju <guimenu>Računi</"
"guimenu>, če je račun odprt v Pogledu glavne knjige. Če je v vašem sistemu "
"nameščen več kot en vtičnik za spletno bančništvo, boste pozvani, katerega "
"uporabiti. Za interno metodo OFX izberite <guimenuitem>&kmymoney; OFX</"
"guimenuitem>. Seznam bank bo prenesen iz interneta in čarovnik vas bo vodil "
"skozi izbiro banke, vnos uporabniškega imena in gesla ter izbiro računa. Če "
"ugotovite, da vaše banke ni na seznamu, boste morda še vedno lahko uporabili "
"ročno možnost. Vaša banka bo morda lahko zagotovila zahtevane parametre ali "
"pa boste morda morali opraviti nekaj raziskav, da jih boste našli."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As implied above, setting up OFX Direct Connect can sometimes be a "
"challenge, especially as the implementations at most institutions do not "
"provide sufficient details in error messages. One particular issue to note "
"is that many institutions require you to change your password the first time "
"you access it online using this method. Unfortunately, at this time, the "
"library that &kmymoney; uses (libofx) does not have a way to interactively "
"change a password. In some cases, it is possible to get a technical support "
"person at the institution to change the password for you. Until we are able "
"to expand this section with more detailed troubleshooting information, if "
"you have trouble getting this to work for you, you can ask for help on the "
"developers' mailing list &devlist; or one of the other <link linkend="
"\"firsttime.contact\"> support channels</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kot je navedeno zgoraj, je nastavitev OFX Direct Connect včasih lahko izziv, "
"zlasti ker izvedbe v večini institucij ne zagotavljajo dovolj podrobnosti v "
"sporočilih o napakah. Ena posebna težava, ki jo je treba omeniti, je, da "
"številne institucije zahtevajo, da spremenite svoje geslo, ko prvič "
"dostopate do njega prek spleta s to metodo. Na žalost je v tem času "
"knjižnica, ki jo &kmymoney; uses (libofx) nima načina za interaktivno "
"spreminjanje gesla. V nekaterih primerih je možno pridobiti osebo tehnične "
"podpore na instituciji, da vam spremeni geslo. Dokler tega razdelka ne bomo "
"razširili s podrobnejšimi informacijami o odpravljanju težav, lahko "
"zaprosite za pomoč na poštnem seznamu razvijalcev &devlist; ali enega od "
"drugih <link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\"> podpornih kanalov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have an account set up with online banking, go to the ledger for "
"that account, and choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Account</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Update account...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will "
"connect to your bank, and download your recent transactions. See the next "
"section on how you can configure the actual date range of transactions to "
"fetch."
msgstr ""
"Ko imate nastavljen račun s spletnim bančništvom, pojdite v glavno knjigo za "
"ta račun in izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Račun</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Posodobi račun...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To bo "
"vzpostavilo povezavo z vašo banko in preneslo vaše nedavne transakcije. "
"Glejte naslednji razdelek o tem, kako lahko konfigurirate dejansko časovno "
"obdobje transakcij, ki jih želite pridobiti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In older versions of &kmymoney;, the Payee name was always taken from the "
"<literal>PAYEEID</literal> field in the OFX data. As of version 4.6, the "
"payee name can be based on either the <literal>PAYEEID</literal>, "
"<literal>NAME</literal>, or <literal>MEMO</literal> field in the OFX "
"transaction. The next section shows how you can configure this feature and "
"some other OFX direct connect settings."
msgstr ""
"V starejših različicah &kmymoney; je bilo ime prejemnika plačila vedno vzeto "
"iz polja <literal>PAYEEID</literal> v podatkih OFX. Od različice 4.6 naprej "
"lahko ime prejemnika plačila temelji na polju <literal>PAYEEID</literal>, "
"<literal>NAME</literal> ali <literal>MEMO</literal> v transakciji OFX. "
"Naslednji razdelek prikazuje, kako lahko konfigurirate to funkcijo in "
"nekatere druge nastavitve neposredne povezave OFX."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring OFX import details"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje podrobnosti uvoza OFX"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This was described previously, in the section on <link linkend=\"details."
"accounts.edit\">editing account details</link>."
msgstr ""
"To je bilo opisano prej v razdelku o <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit"
"\">urejanju podrobnosti računa</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting an OFX file"
msgstr "Izvoz datoteke OFX"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is currently not possible to export your data as an OFX file. If you are "
"interested to contribute in this area, please contact the libofx development "
"team for details."
msgstr ""
"Vaših podatkov trenutno ni mogoče izvoziti kot datoteko OFX. Če želite "
"prispevati na tem področju, se za podrobnosti obrnite na razvojno skupino "
"libofx."

#. Tag: chapter
#: details-impexp.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid "&details-impexp-csv; &details-impexp-woob;"
msgstr "&details-impexp-csv; &details-impexp-woob;"

#~ msgid "2011-07-03"
#~ msgstr "03.07.2011"

#~ msgid "<releaseinfo>4.6</releaseinfo>"
#~ msgstr "<releaseinfo>4.6</releaseinfo>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The &kmymoney; &gnucash; importer handles direct reading of standard "
#~ "(&XML;) files as produced by &gnucash; versions 1.8 and 2.0. The "
#~ "following are not supported:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&kmymoney; &gnucash; uvoznik obravnava neposredno branje standardnih "
#~ "datotek (&XML;), kot jih ustvari &gnucash; različici 1.8 in 2.0. "
#~ "Naslednje ni podprto:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "See <link linkend=\"details.impexp.gncquotes\">\"Online Quotes\"</link> "
#~ "above."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Glejte <link linkend=\"details.impexp.gncquotes\">\"Spletne kotacije\"</"
#~ "link> zgoraj."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In general the default QIF profile should work with your QIF data. In "
#~ "some cases it might become necessary to use a modified QIF profile. See "
#~ "the <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qifimp.profile\">next section</link> "
#~ "for more details on that subject."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Na splošno mora privzeti profil QIF delovati z vašimi podatki QIF. V "
#~ "nekaterih primerih bo morda potrebna uporaba spremenjenega profila QIF. "
#~ "Glejte <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qifimp.profile\">naslednji "
#~ "razdelek</link> za več podrobnosti o tej temi."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The next step is to verify the imported data and accept it. This is a "
#~ "general process and also applies to imports from other sources. It is "
#~ "outlined in a separate section of this document."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Naslednji korak je preverjanje uvoženih podatkov in njihovo sprejemanje. "
#~ "To je splošen postopek in velja tudi za uvoze iz drugih virov. Opisano je "
#~ "v ločenem razdelku tega dokumenta."

#~ msgid "Setting up a QIF profile"
#~ msgstr "Nastavitev profila QIF"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Previous versions of &kmymoney; used to have a tab for date and amount "
#~ "specifications. &kmymoney; now determines those settings by scanning the "
#~ "file. If it cannot figure out all settings, it will interrogate the user "
#~ "during import."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Prejšnje različice &kmymoney; včasih je imel zavihek za specifikacije "
#~ "datuma in zneska. &kmymoney; zdaj določi te nastavitve s skeniranjem "
#~ "datoteke. Če ne more ugotoviti vseh nastavitev, bo med uvozom zaslišal "
#~ "uporabnika."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To use it, edit your favorite QIF Profile, and select the Filter tab. "
#~ "Enter the location of your filter program where prompted. Then, whenever "
#~ "you do a QIF import using this profile, the file you select for importing "
#~ "will be run through your filter first."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Če ga želite uporabiti, uredite svoj najljubši profil QIF in izberite "
#~ "zavihek Filter. Vnesite lokacijo vašega filtrirnega programa, kjer ste "
#~ "pozvani. Nato, kadar koli uvozite QIF s tem profilom, bo datoteka, ki jo "
#~ "izberete za uvoz, najprej prešla skozi vaš filter."

#~ msgid "At the moment, QIF Exporter does not handle export of investments."
#~ msgstr "QIF Exporter se trenutno ne ukvarja z izvozom investicij."

#~ msgid "QIF Export"
#~ msgstr "Izvoz QIF"

#~ msgid "OFX Importer Plugin"
#~ msgstr "Vtičnik OFX Importer"

#~ msgid "Getting the plugin"
#~ msgstr "Pridobivanje vtičnika"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&kmymoney; will import OFX files painlessly. However, this functionality "
#~ "is not built into the core program. You must obtain and install the OFX "
#~ "Importer Plugin. Once that is installed, the command to import OFX files "
#~ "will automatically show up under the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
#~ "<guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&kmymoney; bo neboleče uvozil datoteke OFX. Vendar ta funkcionalnost ni "
#~ "vgrajena v osnovni program. Pridobiti in namestiti morate vtičnik OFX "
#~ "Importer. Ko je to nameščeno, se ukaz za uvoz datotek OFX samodejno "
#~ "prikaže v podmeniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
#~ "<guisubmenu>Uvozi</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Note that many prepackaged versions of &kmymoney; were built with the OFX "
#~ "importer already included or available as a separate package. If the OFX "
#~ "importer does not seem to be installed in your version, the first place "
#~ "to check is in the same place you got your base &kmymoney; package."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Upoštevajte, da veliko predpakiranih različic &kmymoney; so bili izdelani "
#~ "z že vključenim uvoznikom OFX ali na voljo kot ločen paket. Če se zdi, da "
#~ "uvoznik OFX ni nameščen v vaši različici, morate najprej preveriti tam, "
#~ "kjer ste dobili svoj osnovni &kmymoney; paket."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you have installed from RPM, the OFX Importer Plugin is contained "
#~ "within the kmymoney-ofx package. It should be available from whatever "
#~ "source you got the base &kmymoney; package. If you have built from "
#~ "sources, all you need to do is have preferably the libOFX 0.9 development "
#~ "headers and libraries installed on your system. The &kmymoney; build "
#~ "process will detect these and compile the plugin. At the time of release "
#~ "of &kmymoney; 4.6, the latest libofx version was 0.9.4, which is also the "
#~ "minimum required version."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Če ste namestili iz RPM, je vtičnik OFX Importer Plugin v paketu kmymoney-"
#~ "ofx. Na voljo mora biti iz katerega koli vira, kjer ste dobili osnovno "
#~ "&kmymoney; paket. Če ste gradili iz izvorne kode, morate le imeti v "
#~ "sistemu nameščene razvojne glave in knjižnice libOFX 0.9. &kmymoney; "
#~ "postopek izdelave jih bo zaznal in prevedel vtičnik. V času izdaje "
#~ "&kmymoney; 4.6, zadnja različica libofx je bila 0.9.4, kar je tudi "
#~ "najzgodnejša zahtevana različica."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Should you run into trouble trying to compile &kmymoney;, and you are "
#~ "certain you have the correct version of libOFX installed, please contact "
#~ "the developers list &devlist; for assistance. Include a copy of your "
#~ "<filename>config.log</filename> file, compressed first via <command>gzip</"
#~ "command>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Če naletite na težave pri prevajanju &kmymoney; in ste prepričani, da "
#~ "imate nameščeno pravo različico libOFX, se obrnite na seznam razvijalcev "
#~ "&devlist; za pomoč. Vključite kopijo vaše datoteke <filename>config.log</"
#~ "filename>, najprej stisnjene prek <command>gzip</command>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "OFX Direct Connect is now supported in &kmymoney;. This gives you the "
#~ "ability to contact your bank directly to obtain statements. In the "
#~ "future, there will be more help written, and this will be moved to its "
#~ "own section."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "OFX Direct Connect je zdaj podprt v &kmymoney;. Tako se lahko obrnete "
#~ "neposredno na svojo banko in pridobite izpiske. V prihodnosti bo napisana "
#~ "več pomoči in ta bo prestavljena v svoj razdelek."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To enable this feature, you must compile &kmymoney; with the "
#~ "<userinput><option>--enable-ofxbanking</option></userinput> switch (now "
#~ "the default)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, morate prevesti &kmymoney; s stikalom "
#~ "<userinput><option>--enable-ofxbanking</option></userinput> (zdaj "
#~ "privzeto)."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Please be warned: Many banks require a separate signup, will give you a "
#~ "separate password or PIN, and may even charge you a separate fee for this "
#~ "service. No bank directly supports &kmymoney;. You will have to tell them "
#~ "you want to bank directly from <application>MS Money</application> or "
#~ "<application>Quicken</application>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Opozorilo: številne banke zahtevajo ločeno prijavo, dajo vam ločeno geslo "
#~ "ali PIN in vam lahko celo zaračunajo ločeno pristojbino za to storitev. "
#~ "Nobena banka neposredno ne podpira &kmymoney;. Morali jim boste povedati, "
#~ "da želite bančništvo neposredno iz <application>MS Money</application> "
#~ "ali <application>Quicken</application>."

#~ msgid "Writing Importer Plugins"
#~ msgstr "Pisanje vtičnikov za uvoz"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&kmymoney; contains explicit support for importer plugins. If you have a "
#~ "custom format, and you would like to write an importer plugin, we would "
#~ "value your contribution. To do so, you'll need to compile the program "
#~ "from source. Then use the OFX Importer Plugin as an example."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&kmymoney; vsebuje izrecno podporo za vtičnike za uvoznike. Če imate "
#~ "obliko po meri in bi radi napisali vtičnik za uvoz, cenimo vaš prispevek. "
#~ "Če želite to narediti, boste morali program prevesti iz izvorne kode. "
#~ "Nato kot primer uporabite vtičnik OFX Importer."
